《'''Oxenfree'''》是由{{le|夜校工作室|Night School Studio}}（Night School Studio）開發並發行的一款[[驚悚遊戲|驚悚]]風格[[冒險遊戲|冒險]][[独立游戏|獨立]]遊戲。本作首先於2016年1月15日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[OS_X|OS X]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]等平台上發行<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |last=Krankel |first=Sean |date=2016-04-27 |url=https://blog.eu.playstation.com/2016/04/27/supernatural-adventure-oxenfree-possesses-ps4-next-month/ |title=Supernatural adventure Oxenfree possesses PS4 next month |publisher=[[Sony_Computer_Entertainment_Europe|SCEE]] |accessdate=2016-04-27 |archive-date=2016-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160428101345/https://blog.eu.playstation.com/2016/04/27/supernatural-adventure-oxenfree-possesses-ps4-next-month/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後來又分別於同年的5月31日及6月1日發行了[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Linux|Linux]]的版本 <ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://steamcommunity.com/app/388880/discussions/0/451850213953511172/?ctp=5#c350532536099221271|title=Coming to Linux? :: Oxenfree General Discussions|website=steamcommunity.com|accessdate=2016-06-03|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630071423/http://steamcommunity.com/app/388880/discussions/0/451850213953511172/?ctp=5#c350532536099221271|dead-url=no}}</ref>，于2017年10月6日在[[Nintendo_Switch|Nintendo Switch]] eShop上架销售<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/08/31/oxenfree-annonuced-for-nintendo-switch|title=Oxenfree Annonuced for Nintendo Switch|accessdate=2017-10-07|date=2017-08-31|last=Rad|first=Chloi|work=IGN|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007121932/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/08/31/oxenfree-annonuced-for-nintendo-switch|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本遊戲的續作《Oxenfree II: 失落的信號》（英語：Oxenfree II: Lost Signals）目前預計2021年推出。

== 遊戲模式 ==
[[File:Oxenfree_Screenshot.jpg|thumb]]
《Oxenfree》是一款使用[[偽三維|2.5D]]視角的冒險遊戲。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcgamesn.com/oxenfree-devs-collaborate-with-robert-kirkman-to-launch-web-series-and-film-based-on-game|title=Oxenfree devs collaborate with Robert Kirkman, to launch web series and film based on game|website=PCGamesN|access-date=2016-05-27|archive-date=2016-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161117201642/https://www.pcgamesn.com/oxenfree-devs-collaborate-with-robert-kirkman-to-launch-web-series-and-film-based-on-game|dead-url=no}}</ref>遊戲中的對話並無預設的劇本，玩家除了在遊戲中走動之外，還可以在主角艾莉克斯（Alex）有機會說話時從其頭上的數個對話框中選擇想要說的話，或是選擇不說話；而艾莉克斯所說的話也會影響主線劇情的走向，因此也有數種不同的結局。遊戲中的關卡必須透過艾莉克斯的可攜式[[收音機|收音機]]來破解，它的用途包含打開上了鎖的門、聆聽島上的語音導覽或是和遊戲中的鬼魂溝通等等。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/1/15/10760840/oxenfree-review-pc-xbox-one|title=Oxenfree is a spooky '80s teen movie turned into an adventure game|last=Webster|first=Andrew|date=2016-01-15|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|access-date=2016-05-27|archive-date=2016-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160514034550/http://www.theverge.com/2016/1/15/10760840/oxenfree-review-pc-xbox-one|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 劇情 ==
《Oxenfree》的故事背景設定在一座無人定居的觀光小島上，而包含主角艾莉克斯（Alex）在內的一群年輕人在某個夜晚前往島上的沙灘舉辦通宵派對。艾莉克斯在意外地使用她的收音機開啟了一道陰界的裂縫之後，必須想辦法與裂縫中跑出來的鬼魂打交道，同時還得尋找失散在島上各處的其它朋友們。 <ref name="nightschoolstudio.com">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://nightschoolstudio.com/oxenfree/|title=OXENFREE|work=Night School Studio|accessdate=2016-01-16|archive-date=2016-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115115521/http://nightschoolstudio.com/oxenfree/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 開發及發行 ==
遊戲的畫面最先於2015年5月18日在电子游戏网站[[Polygon|Polygon]]上釋出。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |last=Robinson |first=Nick |date=May 18, 2015 |url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/5/18/8621337/oxenfree-gameplay-13-minutes-from-new-2015-adventure-game-night-school-studio-telltale |title=First gameplay from Oxenfree, 2015's coolest-looking adventure game |publisher=[[Polygon|Polygon]] |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archive-date=2016-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123210046/http://www.polygon.com/2015/5/18/8621337/oxenfree-gameplay-13-minutes-from-new-2015-adventure-game-night-school-studio-telltale |dead-url=no }}</ref>直到同年的10月23日，夜校工作室（Night School Studio）與[[微軟|微軟]]共同宣布《Oxenfree》將於2016年1月在[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]和[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]上發行。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |last=Sirani |first=Jordan |date=2015-10-24 |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/10/24/oxenfree-release-window-revealed |title=Oxenfree Release Window Revealed |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archive-date=2017-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826194219/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/10/24/oxenfree-release-window-revealed |dead-url=no }}</ref>遊戲的開發團隊夜校工作室包含了來自[[訴說遊戲|訴說遊戲]]以及[[華特迪士尼公司|迪士尼]]等公司的前任職員，而《Oxenfree》也是該工作室的首作。遊戲的原始藝術由海瑟·格羅斯（Heather Gross）創作，而《{{tsl|en|Tales from the Borderlands|邊緣禁地傳說}}》的首席作家亞當·漢斯（Adam Hines）則負責遊戲的劇本。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://geekandsundry.com/is-oxenfree-the-first-great-indie-game-of-2016/|title=Is Oxenfree the First Great Indie Game of 2016? {{!}} Geek and Sundry|date=2016-01-12|website=Geek and Sundry|access-date=2016-05-27|archive-date=2016-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807192347/http://geekandsundry.com/is-oxenfree-the-first-great-indie-game-of-2016/|dead-url=no}}</ref>為遊戲擔任配音的成員則包括艾維塔·艾許（Avital Ash）、布-{里}-塔妮·強森（Britanni Johnson）、{{tsl|en|Gavin Hammon|蓋文·哈蒙}}、{{tsl|en|Erin Yvette|艾琳·伊薇特}}、亞倫·庫班（Aaron Kuban）及喬·齊葉雅（Joe Zieja）等人。<ref name="nightschoolstudio.com"/>

《Oxenfree》發行時，則有標準版和收藏版兩種版本。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |last=Evangelho |first=Jason |date=2016-01-14 |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/jasonevangelho/2016/01/14/the-collectors-edition-for-oxenfree-is-perfect-and-we-need-more-like-it/#2715e4857a0b328bd2521f9b |title=The Collector's Edition For 'Oxenfree' Is Perfect, And We Need More Like It |publisher=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archive-date=2016-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117094830/http://www.forbes.com/sites/jasonevangelho/2016/01/14/the-collectors-edition-for-oxenfree-is-perfect-and-we-need-more-like-it/#2715e4857a0b328bd2521f9b |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 實境遊戲 ==
在遊戲中，玩家透過收音機在島上各處找到的隱藏頻道的頻率數字可以組成一個真實世界中的電話號碼。這組電話號碼的線索指向一個[[推特|推特]]帳號@xray9169363733，該帳號曾發布許多加密的訊息，而這些訊息則似乎指向一個真實世界中的地點。2016年5月7日，[[YouTube|YouTube]]用戶傑西·考克斯（Jesse Cox）發布了他所收到該推特帳號寄出的一部《Oxenfree》的[[PS4|PS4]]版本預告片；他所收到的預告片和[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]在其官方YouTube頻道發布的版本相似，除了結尾有部分字母被標上紅底，而那些紅底的字母則指向網站[https://web.archive.org/web/20181120063523/http://edwardsisland.com/ www.edwardsisland.com]。網站中又有一些訊息被發現，其中最重要的一則是「MILNER IS WARD」，也證實了玩家的懷疑——某項特別的物品已被藏在[[華盛頓州|華盛頓州]][[班布里治島_(華盛頓州)|班布里治島]]上的{{tsl|en|Fort Ward (Washington)|沃德堡}}中。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://telkomgaming.co.za/there-is-something-special-going-on-with-oxenfree/|title=There is Something Special Going on with Oxenfree {{!}} Telkom Gaming|website=telkomgaming.co.za|access-date=2016-05-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160521111244/http://telkomgaming.co.za/there-is-something-special-going-on-with-oxenfree/|archivedate=2016-05-21}}</ref>

